    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh i know, i just really hate waiting at the urgant care and the deductible is so high. i don't think it's broken, it just feels really tender right where the bone is. if i just keep it iced and wrapped tight and stay off it for like 3 or 4 days, isnt that basically the same thing as what a doctor would do anyway? like, if it's just a bad sprain, won't it feel better by then?",
