      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but inflamation is what i'm worried about most right now. i have some ibuprofen in the cabinet, can i just take a few of those every 4 hours to keep the swelling down and just wait it out? i feel like if i can just get the pain under control with some meds and the ice, i can just stay on the couch for a few days and it'll be fine. it's probably just a bad bruise or something, right?",
